				<h2 class="title icon icon0">
					Re: Patent Troll reboot... Sue the end user.
				</h2>
				

						
						
				<div class="content">
					<div id="post_message_1768266">
						<blockquote class="postcontent restore ">
							I'm a big fan of the idea of patents - being an R&amp;D guy I want to have my inventions protected. But this is ridiculous. Chain the patent to the inventor and require any prosecutor that wants to litigate patent law to present the inventor in court or have the case be dismissed. Specifically forbid subpoenaing the patent holder - that way the assholes doing this have to at least pay the inventor enough that they'll show up, and should the inventor die the patent becomes public domain.
						</blockquote>
					</div>

					
